<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>صاحبَه <span class="c2">(قتله)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> "، فعلاه الزبير <span class="c2">(فقتله)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span>، <span class="c2">(ثم جاء)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span> بسلبه فنفله النبي <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">(إياه)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
